snippet.title: Shatter PSN release trailer
snippet.description:
Main trailer for Shatter PSN, an original title from Sidhe, available from 23 July 2009 for US$7.99.

For more information on Shatter, see http://www.shattergame.com

For the Shatter soundtrack see http://sidhe.bandcamp.com/
